They could let Paladins keep Thunder of Karana but then they would have to redesign and design all encounters with this ability in mind just like they do with CH and defensive.<br>
<br>
I think Verant has gone overboard with trying to continually add things to make players uber.  Is that all that people play this game for?  If they can't get more uber will they quit, is that Verant's thinking, it seems to be the case. I keep playing and I haven't upgraded any of my stuff in months, I just enjoy playing with friends and having a good time.  I just get disappointed sometime that unless you are the &quot;must be uber&quot; type that you miss out on some content of the game.<br>
<br>
I've been play 10 months now, I'd love to hear about how the game was before and after these changes, and how the skill/spells were nerfed or whatever after they realized they were too much.<br>
